  "text": "General molecular cloning was performed according to standard methods [CITATION_1] . When polymerase chain reaction (PCR) or site-specific mutagenesis was involved in subcloning, the constructs were sequenced to confirm that no mistakes were generated. Sitedirected mutagenesis and DNA and RNA gel blot hybridization were performed as described previously [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
